From the results of exact soluble model, we suggest a phase diagram of our
model as sketched in Fig. .  We will show that
the phase diagram contains four
different string condensed phases and one string non-condensed phase. All the
phases have the same symmetry and are distinguished only by their different
quantum orders.

Let us first discuss the phase with . We will assume
